Resource Profile: FR Core Organization Profile

Official URL: https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/StructureDefinition/fr-core-organization Version: 2.2.0-ballot
Active as of 2025-12-09 Computable Name: FRCoreOrganizationProfile

Profile of the Organization resource for France. This profile specifies the types of identifiers for organizations in France, and adds a number of French extensions.

Profil de la ressource Organization pour la France. Ce profil spécifie les types d’identifiants pour l’organisation en France, et ajoute des extensions françaises.

Utilisations:

  • Référer à ce Profil: FR Core Appointment Operator Extension, FR Core Encounter Profile, FR Core Healthcare Service Profile, FR Core Location Profile... Show 15 more, FR Core Observation Bmi Profile, FR Core Observation Body Height Profile, FR Core Observation Body Temperature Profile, FR Core Observation Body Weight Profile, FR Core Observation Blood Pressure Profile, FR Core Observation Head Circum Profile, FR Core Observation Heart Rate Profile, FR Core Observation Respiratory Rate Profile, FR Core Observation Oxygen Saturation Profile, FR Core Organization Pole Profile, FR Core Organization UAC Profile, FR Core Organization UF Profile, FR Core Organization Profile, FR Core Patient Profile and FR Core Practitioner Role
  • Exemples pour ce Profil: HOPITAL INTERCOMMUNAL DE LA PRESQU'ILE G

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
